title: 02/22/22 DPS Hour 3 - Rob Parker & Mike Harmon Guest Hosting
itunes:title: 02/22/22 DPS Hour 3 - Rob Parker & Mike Harmon Guest Hosting
description:
Rob Parker and Mike Harmon, in for Doug, react to Aaron Rodgers' cryptic Instagram post and discuss what will happen next for the reigning MVP. 10-year NBA Veteran Ryan Hollins joins the guys to look ahead to the second half of the NBA season. Plus, the guys highlight the wildest stories in sports from the last few days!
